OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F422A1775239865
OL,3,CHealth and educational sites to get
OL,4,Cspiking test kits in pilot scheme
OL,6,FVictims of spiking will be able to
OL,7,Fmore easily access testing kits in
OL,8,FNewcastle city centre venues as part
OL,9,Fof a new pilot scheme.
OL,11,FThe test will detect and identify
OL,12,Fsubstances known to be used in spiking
OL,13,Fincidents. Following the scheme's
OL,14,Flaunch, they will be more readily
OL,15,Favailable in places such as health and
OL,16,Feducational sites.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/8
