OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,423,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F422A1775239865
OL,3,CHealth and educational sites to get
OL,4,Cspiking test kits in pilot scheme
OL,6,FThe kits are to help offer victims
OL,7,Fmore options for support, with police
OL,8,Fencouraging those who think they have
OL,9,Fbeen spiked to get tested even if they
OL,10,Fdo not want to pursue the issue
OL,11,Fthrough the criminal justice system.
OL,12,FThe goal is to improve the accuracy of
OL,13,Freported spiking statistics.
OL,15,FColin Mackie, founder of the charity
OL,16,FSpike Aware UK, said the pilot is a
OL,17,Fgreat step forward.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,423,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F422A1775239865
OL,3,CHealth and educational sites to get
OL,4,Cspiking test kits in pilot scheme
OL,6,FHe said: "It's going to give victims
OL,7,Fmore confidence to come forward, where
OL,8,Fit's not held all within a police
OL,9,Fstation and a police environment.
OL,11,F"I think they'll feel more relaxed and
OL,12,Fmore confident to come forward and
OL,13,Freport if they think they've been
OL,14,Fspiked."
OL,16,FHe also hopes it'll improve public
OL,17,Fknowledge of what substances are used
OL,18,Ffor spiking as the lack of current
OL,19,Freports lead to uncertainty.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
