OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,423,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F422A1775239865
OL,3,CHealth and educational sites to get
OL,4,Cspiking test kits in pilot scheme
OL,6,FThe scheme is led by the Home Office
OL,7,Fand National Centre for Violence
OL,8,FAgainst Women and Girls and Public
OL,9,FProtection (NCVPP). It will be rolled
OL,10,Fout if it proves to increase the
OL,11,Fnumber of victims coming forward.
OL,13,FDetective Chief Superintendent Claire
OL,14,FHammond, VAWG delivery lead at the
OL,15,FNCVPP, said: "We hope that by
OL,16,Fproviding direct access to testing we
OL,17,Fwill empower victims with a choice
OL,18,Fover the support they receive and help
OL,19,Fthem get answers. If something doesn't
OL,20,Ffeel right, then please seek support
OL,21,Fand come forward for a test.
OL,26,@wD@NOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,423,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F422A1775239865
OL,3,CHealth and educational sites to get
OL,4,Cspiking test kits in pilot scheme
OL,6,F"Spiking has a significant impact of
OL,7,Ffeelings of safety, particularly for
OL,8,Fwomen and girls, and we are absolutely
OL,9,Ffocused on tackling it. It is,
OL,10,Ftherefore, crucial that we know and
OL,11,Funderstand when and where it is
OL,12,Fhappening, so we can use that
OL,13,Fintelligence to prevent further cases
OL,14,Fand disrupt offenders."
OL,16,FSuperintendent Joanne Park-Simmons, of
OL,17,FNorthumbria Police said the force
OL,18,Frecognises the distress and worry
OL,19,Fvictims of spiking experience, adding,
OL,20,F"Ultimately, we want people to know
OL,21,Fwe're here to help them.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@WO]|D@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,423,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F422A1775239865
OL,3,CHealth and educational sites to get
OL,4,Cspiking test kits in pilot scheme
OL,6,F"We're proud to have been selected as
OL,7,Fone of three police forces in the
OL,8,Fcountry for this new pilot, which we
OL,9,Fhope will only strengthen our response
OL,10,Fto such incidents going forward.
OL,12,F"By working in collaboration with our
OL,13,Fpartners in Newcastle, including
OL,14,Fhealth and education settings, we can
OL,15,Ffurther understand the bigger picture
OL,16,Fand ensure those affected are
OL,17,Fsupported in a way that suits them.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,423,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F422A1775239865
OL,3,CHealth and educational sites to get
OL,4,Cspiking test kits in pilot scheme
OL,6,F"We know that not everyone wants to
OL,7,Fprogress a criminal outcome, but it's
OL,8,Fhugely important we can understand
OL,9,Fwhat is happening in our area, so we
OL,10,Fcan take more action.
OL,12,F"Newcastle has always been a safe and
OL,13,Fwelcoming city ` and we want to make
OL,14,Fsure it stays that way. If you think
OL,15,Fyou have unfortunately experienced
OL,16,Fspiking, please consider accessing a
OL,17,Ftest through a provider near you.
OL,19,F"You will be listened to, and as ever
OL,20,Fwe'll be here if you need us."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOU{D@AOU|D@^O]
